This is Perl module Text::ClearSilver, a Perl binding to the ClearSilver
template engine.

INSTALLATION

Text::ClearSilver installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up,
you should just be able to do

    $ cpan Text::ClearSilver

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    $ perl Makefile.PL
    $ make && make test

Then install it:

    $ make install

DOCUMENTATION

Text::ClearSilver documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    $ perldoc Text::ClearSilver

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

